ly-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"> <div class=\"notecard obsolete\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Veraltet:</strong> Dieses Feature ist veraltet. Obwohl es in manchen Browsern immer noch funktioniert, wird von seiner Benutzung abgeraten, da es jederzeit entfernt werden kann. Es sollte daher nicht mehr verwendet werden.</p></div></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Starting in <span title=\"(Firefox 6.0 / Thunderbird 6.0 / SeaMonkey 2.3)\">Gecko&nbsp;6.0</span>,<code> document.width </code>is no longer supported. Instead, use <code>document.body.clientWidth</code>. See <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/clientWidth\"><code>element.clientWidth</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Gibt die Breite des <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a> Elements des aktuellen Dokuments in Pixeln zurück.</p>\n\n<p>Wird nicht vom Internet Explorer unterstützt.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>pixels</em> = document.width;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Die Breite des Dokuments beträgt \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>width <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" Pixel.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"alternatives","title":"Alternativen","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">document.body.clientWidth              /* Breite des &lt;body&gt; */\ndocument.documentElement.clientWidth   /* Breite des &lt;html&gt; */\nwindow.innerWidth                      /* Breite des Browserfensters */\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<p>HTML5</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/height\"><code>document.height</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/clientWidth\"><code>Element.clientWidth</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element/scrollWidth\"><code>Element.scrollWidth</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"example"},{"text":"Alternativen","id":"alternatives"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"specification"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Gibt die Breite des <body> Elements des aktuellen Dokuments in Pixeln zurück.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document.width","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Document.width","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.width","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"document.width","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"document.width","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Document.width","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/document/width","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/document/width/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Document","title":"Document"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/width","title":"Document.width"}],"pageTitle":"Document.width - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}